<hr local-id=3D"7016a0a3-8253-4c67-88c5-e20eb5b987a0">
<ol start=3D"9" local-id=3D"932efe6b211c">
<li local-id=3D"8731405ecf70">
<p local-id=3D"d8a0ca311558"><strong>Conclusion</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"896fa1e349d6">This requirement analysis defines a structured=
 approach for automating AWS infrastructure operations using Jenkins.</p>
<p local-id=3D"40b82b6a36be">The implemented solution demonstrates:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"053f3dff-4e98-4133-8ea8-d5dca3f9a4df">
<li local-id=3D"7bb045c6-934b-4072-b674-ceea792d9325">
<p local-id=3D"888fc9071843">Automated lifecycle management of EC2 resource=
s</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0eaa0886-2c89-497f-8094-b02245eba5c1">
<p local-id=3D"825d42cc0f77">Controlled scaling of container services</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"fbfb9d0b-e36b-4a70-a0cb-fad8c27072bc">
<p local-id=3D"9e419aa49af0">Secure IAM-based authentication</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2c74c399-5712-4c76-a9e7-03268107eca3">
<p local-id=3D"a8c5c2baeb0f">Cost-conscious operational strategy</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f556a325-3e75-4d6c-84bc-24bf72bf3144">
<p local-id=3D"972c4c6294c8">Standardized DevOps automation practices</p></=
li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ddc956b4ed1a">The integration of Jenkins with AWS services e=
stablishes a reliable and secure foundation for infrastructure automation w=
ithin a cloud environment.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ba7c77ac6fc8">&nbsp;</p>
